\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
}{}$w$\end{document}</tex-math></inline-formula> of a given length the number of sequences that contain <inline-formula><tex-math id="M9">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
